metadata.name: Birds of Paradise
metadata.description:
1/1 video from Lost Eden, an 8 part visual narrative series exploring the human condition through the modern adaption of the story of the Fall. 

Director: Olivia Burgess & Jean Claude Billmaier

DOP: Dominic Miller

Producer: Olivia Burgess & Ben Schaub

Dancer/Choreographer: Olivia Burgess & Emily Paige Anderson

Editor: Nathalie Basoski

Original Score: Clem Lo

Costume: George Reynolds


*Collector to receive 4k format upon auction settlement. 

*Funds from sales to be split up between the team.
